transcripts.text: Hi, I'm Carolyn Mace and welcome to Gaia Live Events.  I am honored to be the first woman presenter in this exciting new conscious venue nestled at the foot of the Rocky Mountains in colorful Colorado.  Join me this August for an extraordinary two and a half days of exclusive new teachings as we break down the five greatest personal and spiritual challenges we face today.  Looking forward to seeing you soon.  Thank you.
